---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <section class="container" style="padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md); max-width: 720px;">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--ink-muted);">
      Sowthri · GenAI Architect · Dammam, Saudi Arabia.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
      I design and build GenAI platforms for heavy industry — refining, petrochemicals, utilities, and mining. My focus is end-to-end architectural capability · not one-off proofs of concept.
    </p>

    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Platform before payload.</strong> The substrate comes first · then use cases inherit it.</li>
      <li><strong>Production-ready in design · portfolio-economical in operation.</strong> Every pattern could scale · spend stays under $25.</li>
      <li><strong>Full public source.</strong> Nothing private · nothing hidden. Two GitHub repositories · everything reviewable.</li>
      <li><strong>Ephemeral by design (ADR-0013).</strong> Azure endpoints spin up per demo · tear down after · $0.50 per session.</li>
      <li><strong>Deliberate failure branches (ADR-0011).</strong> Three permanent branches show the pipeline's gates firing. Not theater.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Regional context</h2>
    <p>
      Based in Dammam · Regional market fluency. Portfolio includes ALLaM (SDAIA's Arabic-English model) integration as a regional signal.
    </p>

    <h2 id="contact">Get in touch</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--ink-muted);">
      Open to GenAI Architect roles in Saudi Arabia, GCC, and remote. Available for contract, full-time, or consulting engagements.
    </p>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs); margin-top: var(--space-md);">
      <a href="mailto:sowthri.industrial.ai@gmail.com" style="padding: var(--space-sm); background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--grid-line); border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink);">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">EMAIL</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 0.3em;">sowthri.industrial.ai@gmail.com</div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sowthri-somasundaram" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="padding: var(--space-sm); background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--grid-line); border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink);">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">LINKEDIN</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 0.3em;">in/sowthri-somasundaram</div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/sowthri-industrial-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="padding: var(--space-sm); background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--grid-line); border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink);">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">GITHUB</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 0.3em;">@sowthri-industrial-ai</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: var(--space-md); font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--ink-muted);">
      <strong>Interview availability:</strong> I can spin up the live Azure environment in ~8 minutes · ~$0.50 burn rate per session · tears down automatically (ADR-0013). Just reach out.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
